<Default><b>[Frieren sighs]</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:31.110 --> 00:02:33.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Would it kill her
to listen to what I have to say</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:34.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once in a while before
