c0000025
00:02:35.660 --> 00:02:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. What's all the noise about?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:38.410 --> 00:02:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lovebirds fighting?</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:41.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:41.490 --> 00:02:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you weren’t aware,
today is Fern’s birthday.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:44.370 --> 00:02:47.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And unfortunately, Stark forgot
to get her a gift.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
She’s not taking it well.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:49.090 --> 00:02:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:50.420 --> 00:02:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:52.170 --> 00:02:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you ask me, you were
a bit too harsh this time.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:57.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You never listen
to a single thing</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:57.140 --> 00:02:58.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that poor lad has to say.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:00.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scowls]</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:01.060 --> 00:03:03.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest, I didn’t
get you anything, either.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it comes to us men,</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:07.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we couldn’t care less about
trivial dates, you know.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:07.820 --> 00:03:09.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Anniversaries, birthdays...
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:09.730 --> 00:03:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sein grunts]
That hurt! I get it</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:13.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, I-I’ll go
pick up a trinket</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:15.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for your birthday
if you’ll stop!</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:15.450 --> 00:03:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least spare my knees!</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:17.620 --> 00:03:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:19.870 --> 00:03:20.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After that beating,
I feel even more sorry for him.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:25.670 --> 00:03:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’m old enough now
not to make a big stink</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if somebody hurts my feelings,</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:29.340 --> 00:03:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but a girl like you
has the power</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to stir up the emotions
of a boy like him</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:32.710 --> 00:03:33.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into a whirlwind.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:34.710 --> 00:03:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:41.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My advice is to go
after the kid.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:47.230 --> 00:03:49.060 line:90% align:center
