c0000064
00:04:26.350 --> 00:04:28.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A cute pouch you’ve got there.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:29.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] You don't like it?</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:29.850 --> 00:04:30.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I don’t like how used</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:31.060 --> 00:04:33.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to keeping the company
of women you seem.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:33.270 --> 00:04:34.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sein groans] Of course.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:35.820 --> 00:04:37.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, did you ever find Stark?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:40.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I spotted him in the plaza.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:41.070 --> 00:04:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Couldn’t bring yourself
to talk to him, could ya?</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:44.070 --> 00:04:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:45.710 --> 00:04:46.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:47.080 --> 00:04:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It’s not that
you don’t like the guy.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just aren’t used
to keeping the company of men</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:51.330 --> 00:04:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your own age.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:52.750 --> 00:04:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, to be young!</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:54.970 --> 00:04:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter.
Choose whatever you want.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:57.930 --> 00:04:59.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can take a look
at some other shops, too.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:02.630 --> 00:05:05.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks,
but that’s quite all right.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:09.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine. Guess I’ll choose
on my own.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:10.690 --> 00:05:12.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, if he did forget
to get you something,</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:13.020 --> 00:05:14.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don’t take it personally.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:14.770 --> 00:05:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He doesn’t strike me
as the conscientious type.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:17.780 --> 00:05:18.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt there are many years</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:18.950 --> 00:05:20.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he even remembers
his own birthday.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:21.110 --> 00:05:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don’t blame the fool.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:23.450 --> 00:05:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He didn’t have to remember,</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I gave him
a present on it.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You picked out one together,
didn’t you?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:30.460 --> 00:05:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you know that?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:32.660 --> 00:05:33.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Most people
wouldn’t decline</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when someone offers
to buy them whatever they want.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:37.050 --> 00:05:39.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must already have
some birthday shopping memory</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:40.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you consider sacred.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:42.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That’s why you told me no.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:45.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess that could be.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don’t know about sacred,</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:46.810 --> 00:05:48.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it did feel like
the right choice.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:49.180 --> 00:05:50.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe it.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:51.230 --> 00:05:52.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, apologize to Stark,</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:52.980 --> 00:05:55.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then you two can pick out
the best present in town.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:57.940 --> 00:06:01.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure, he’s slow on the uptake,
but he’s just a kid.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:03.860 --> 00:06:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want to make up
with him, yes?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:06.620 --> 00:06:08.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Remember that people
can’t know how you feel</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:08.700 --> 00:06:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until you tell them.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess you’re right.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:15.170 --> 00:06:16.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’m gonna head back
to the inn, now.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:16.630 --> 00:06:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-One thing.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:18.340 --> 00:06:20.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’m sorry
about all the kicking.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:20.510 --> 00:06:27.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:39.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] Mister Stark?
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Fern.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:47.450 --> 00:06:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Stark groans]
-[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:50.410 --> 00:06:51.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I--
-Sorry!</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:54.660 --> 00:06:56.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, I wanted to choose a gift</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:58.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with you to make sure
you’d love it.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:58.500 --> 00:06:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But after you got upset,</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:59.750 --> 00:07:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn’t want it to look like
I was trying to dig myself</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>out of a hole,
so I didn’t say anything...</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I got nervous,</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:06.430 --> 00:07:09.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I was worried you might
become even more mad at me.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:10.890 --> 00:07:13.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That wouldn’t have made me mad
in the slightest.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:13.930 --> 00:07:15.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:15.900 --> 00:07:17.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you forgive me?</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:19.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was too harsh with you.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:20.980 --> 00:07:24.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] Please.
I’ve grown used to it.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:24.650 --> 00:07:26.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I really
am sorry, though.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:29.410 --> 00:07:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You ready to shop?</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:31.410 --> 00:07:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:33.530 --> 00:07:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:34.870 --> 00:07:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:50.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Spying
on the sweethearts?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:50.510 --> 00:07:52.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's in poor taste, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You’re doing the same.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I’m just glad that
they made up.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:00.610 --> 00:08:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The older you get,
the better you start</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:02.440 --> 00:08:03.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>understanding relationships,</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:03.940 --> 00:08:06.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the better you can do that,
the fewer conflicts arise.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:09.410 --> 00:08:11.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Arguments like that
are a privilege of the young.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:12.700 --> 00:08:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This can't have been
easy for you, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:15.540 --> 00:08:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking after two kids
all alone?</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You understand relationships?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:21.710 --> 00:08:23.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Make that three kids.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It struck me as odd
Fern turned to me for advice</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:30.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>instead of you.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:31.640 --> 00:08:32.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A girl wouldn’t do that</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>unless she has someone
in her past</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:34.180 --> 00:08:36.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she’s comparing me to.
[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:36.650 --> 00:08:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] You do know Fern
was raised</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:38.310 --> 00:08:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by Heiter, don’t you?</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:39.690 --> 00:08:42.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] That’s the last person
I should be compared to.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:42.270 --> 00:08:43.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was a great priest.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:43.850 --> 00:08:46.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>“Great” isn’t the word
I would use.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:46.530 --> 00:08:49.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] When he wasn’t drunk,
he was deathly hungover.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:51.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
He’s gone undead on us.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:53.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] He was terribly picky
with his food.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:54.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quit it, Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:54.490 --> 00:08:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] And he lied
more often than not.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:56.290 --> 00:08:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven’t had a drop all day!</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was a corrupt priest,
plain and simple.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:01.710 --> 00:09:04.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I admit,
your depravity far exceeds his.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:06.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, sorry about that.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:09.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that stuff
is hard to believe.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:11.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds nothing like
the Heiter I remember.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:14.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was a kind, dependable,
and upright old man.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:15.190 --> 00:09:16.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
A proper grown-up.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:16.730 --> 00:09:18.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The very opposite
of what I’ve become.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:23.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The years
have changed you, Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:23.810 --> 00:09:25.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You’ve grown dignified.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:25.490 --> 00:09:26.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:27.070 --> 00:09:28.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER (OLD)] To me
that sounds like a nice way</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:28.950 --> 00:09:30.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of saying “old.”</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:30.780 --> 00:09:34.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A certain level of maturity
comes naturally as we age.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or rather, that’s what I wish
I could say.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:38.330 --> 00:09:40.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truth is, though my body
has grown and shrunk,</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:40.910 --> 00:09:43.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my mind has hardly changed
since I was a child.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've pretended
to be an adult all my life.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:46.550 --> 00:09:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I might look
the part now,</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:50.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not a bit of adulthood
has stirred within me.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:53.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’d like to be
a proper grown-up,</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:56.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I fear I’ll pretend
until I die.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:59.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It’s important
that children have adults.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:59.230 --> 00:10:02.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Little ones can’t thrive
without emotional support.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:04.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern is the hardworking sort.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:08.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She needs a lot of guidance
and a lot of praise.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you’re still a child,
then shouldn’t you be praised</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:11.780 --> 00:10:13.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for maintaining this ruse?</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:13.190 --> 00:10:14.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where’s the grown-up
to praise you?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She’s up above somewhere,
waiting for me to join her.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:20.250 --> 00:10:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to venture
into heaven</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:21.700 --> 00:10:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before I receive my reward.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:23.910 --> 00:10:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, while you’re still here,
I could always praise you.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:30.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You’d do that for me?
How kind.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I doubt you understand</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:32.010 --> 00:10:34.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just how a withering human
like me might feel.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:35.180 --> 00:10:36.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So how do you intend
to praise me?</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:47.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:49.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] I must admit,</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:49.780 --> 00:10:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that was much nicer
than I expected.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:52.780 --> 00:10:55.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren. Once I get to heaven,</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:58.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’ll have a word
with the Goddess for you.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:58.740 --> 00:10:59.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you join me,</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:59.990 --> 00:11:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you should be praised by her,
too, my friend.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Oh?
Then I'll look forward to it.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:09.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:10.210 --> 00:11:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:12.420 --> 00:11:14.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] What do you think
you're doing, Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:17.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my opinion, you’re as proper
as grown-ups come, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:19.390 --> 00:11:20.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:23.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sein inhales and exhales]</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:23.850 --> 00:11:25.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] If only you were
an older lady,</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:25.610 --> 00:11:27.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this moment would be perfect.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:27.730 --> 00:11:29.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You should be glad, then.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:29.820 --> 00:11:31.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Precious few women
are older than me.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:35.910 --> 00:11:38.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:41.490 --> 00:11:42.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, sir.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:44.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This area has
an extreme deficit</b></Default>

c0000225
00:11:44.830 --> 00:11:46.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of passenger carriages.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:46.210 --> 00:11:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We must all help our fellow man
in times of need.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:49.090 --> 00:11:50.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I work as merchant</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:50.420 --> 00:11:52.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>selling my ware
in the town up ahead.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:52.710 --> 00:11:55.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I supply the people there
with fine accessories.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:57.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at my stock if you’d like.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:57.510 --> 00:11:59.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You’re quite the salesman,
aren’t you?</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:59.970 --> 00:12:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alas, finer things
are lost on me.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:02.640 --> 00:12:04.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My apprentice Fern
may be interested, though.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Did you buy
a new bracelet?</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:10.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Well, uh...</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] Kind of.
-[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:13.690 --> 00:12:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That's a pretty design.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:15.620 --> 00:12:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a ring with
the very same pattern on it.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:18.530 --> 00:12:21.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a gift from Himmel
for a job well done.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:21.530 --> 00:12:23.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think
it would match perfectly.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:23.410 --> 00:12:24.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’ve never seen it.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Let me think.
Where did I put that thing?</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:28.210 --> 00:12:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clattering]
-[FRIEREN] Under here?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:32.290 --> 00:12:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:36.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goodness.
You’re so disorganized.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:37.090 --> 00:12:38.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Finally.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:39.890 --> 00:12:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:42.510 --> 00:12:45.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000249
00:12:47.850 --> 00:12:48.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:51.690 --> 00:12:54.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Sorry.
I let my guard down.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:55.270 --> 00:12:57.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Avian monsters
are cunning beasts,</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and very skilled
at concealing their mana.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What to do.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Let’s defeat
the monster</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:04.490 --> 00:13:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then figure something out.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:06.290 --> 00:13:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mages use magic
to fly around all the time.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can make a carriage float
for a bit, can’t you?</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:12.210 --> 00:13:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:13.540 --> 00:13:15.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever seen
a flying carriage before?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:15.930 --> 00:13:17.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Yeah.
We’re in one right now</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:18.090 --> 00:13:19.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] This may come
as a surprise,</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:20.180 --> 00:13:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it has only been
40 short years</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:22.050 --> 00:13:24.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since humankind
first learned how to fly.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:25.050 --> 00:13:27.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until then, the skies
were the exclusive domain</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of demons and monsters.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:29.690 --> 00:13:31.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The flying magic
you see us use today</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:31.980 --> 00:13:35.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is actually a demon spell
mankind was able to repurpose.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:35.140 --> 00:13:37.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody’s looking
for a lecture, okay?</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:37.150 --> 00:13:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So can you make
the carriage levitate, or not?</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:40.150 --> 00:13:41.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can’t adapt their spell,</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because we’ve merely
copied the “how”</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:44.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without understanding
the “why.”</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:45.540 --> 00:13:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Things larger than humans</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:46.830 --> 00:13:49.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can only be made to fly
in short spurts.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should’ve led with that.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:50.910 --> 00:13:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We’ll have to abandon ship.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’ll fly out
with our new merchant ally.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:55.510 --> 00:13:57.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Fern, you leave with Sein.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:57.340 --> 00:13:58.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understood, ma’am.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:58.760 --> 00:14:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MERCHANT 13A]
I'll get my cargo together.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:00.510 --> 00:14:03.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh... Hey, uh, and me?</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:03.380 --> 00:14:05.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured that
you could jump down.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:05.260 --> 00:14:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:06.980 --> 00:14:08.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pretty sure a fall like that
would kill me.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Surely a warrior can
handle a fall from this height.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:11.390 --> 00:14:13.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh! Don’t look at me
like I’m crazy!</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:13.270 --> 00:14:14.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know good and well
that would snap</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:14.430 --> 00:14:15.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>every bone in my body!</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:15.690 --> 00:14:17.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really think it would?</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:17.610 --> 00:14:19.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Eisen could
free-fall from any height</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:21.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without getting so much
as a scratch.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:22.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thudding]
-[Heiter screams]</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:28.620 --> 00:14:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
What is wrong with this man?</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:31.160 --> 00:14:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Heiter was appalled.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:35.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet another story
that goes to show</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:35.330 --> 00:14:37.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how far from normal
Mister Eisen is.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:38.510 --> 00:14:41.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps we can levitate
the carriage for a moment,</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:41.130 --> 00:14:43.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just before it crashes
into the forest.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:43.460 --> 00:14:44.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’d need to calculate</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:44.590 --> 00:14:46.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I have the power to stop
a free-fall.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:47.270 --> 00:14:49.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I can’t sufficiently reduce
the force of our plummet,</b></Default>

c0000304
00:14:49.970 --> 00:14:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we’d be ground
into minced meat.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:53.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Why’d you have
to say it all scary-like?</b></Default>

c0000306
00:14:54.350 --> 00:14:57.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever it is that we do,
we should probably do it quick.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:14:58.190 --> 00:15:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This type of monster
kills its prey</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:00.190 --> 00:15:01.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by slamming it
into the ground.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:03.150 --> 00:15:04.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:04.230 --> 00:15:11.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:13.660 --> 00:15:14.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:16.420 --> 00:15:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Well, I suppose
her idea is worth a shot.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:19.170 --> 00:15:21.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:21.210 --> 00:15:23.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You better not drop us!</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:26.260 --> 00:15:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:28.260 --> 00:15:31.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] We’re alive.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:37.570 --> 00:15:40.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Indeed. Indicating
our plan was a success.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:40.230 --> 00:15:41.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
You call that a success?</b></Default>

c0000320
00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:43.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What’s worse is
she called it a “plan.”</b></Default>

c0000321
00:15:46.620 --> 00:15:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Your horse
was only slightly injured,</b></Default>

c0000322
00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:49.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I fixed it up for you.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:15:49.830 --> 00:15:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The greater concern
is your carriage.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:15:51.620 --> 00:15:53.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It needs major repairs.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:15:53.740 --> 00:15:54.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:15:54.910 --> 00:15:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, don’t apologize.
I’m thankful.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:15:56.960 --> 00:15:59.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it had just been me,
I would surely be dead.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:15:59.710 --> 00:16:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] It’s gonna take
some time to fix the carriage.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:02.790 --> 00:16:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:17.110 --> 00:16:19.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
It should be right here.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:20.810 --> 00:16:22.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder where it went.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:23.560 --> 00:16:25.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[saw hissing]</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:25.740 --> 00:16:27.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] It's gotten
a lot warmer lately.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:28.200 --> 00:16:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might be time
to start dressing lighter.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:30.700 --> 00:16:32.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, by the way, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
About that bracelet...</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:33.990 --> 00:16:35.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, right.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:35.490 --> 00:16:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is what Mister Stark
got me for my birthday.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spent three whole hours
picking out that thing.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:41.040 --> 00:16:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you ended up
being the one to choose?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:46.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted him to pick whatever
he thought would be best.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:46.590 --> 00:16:49.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.
Should’ve seen that coming.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:16:49.760 --> 00:16:51.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] She put you through
the wringer, huh?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:16:51.890 --> 00:16:53.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her type is the hardest
to deal with.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:16:54.260 --> 00:16:55.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Truth.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:16:57.100 --> 00:16:58.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about this one?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:16:59.270 --> 00:17:02.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Three hours of trying
to gauge her reactions.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:02.600 --> 00:17:04.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt like I was dying inside.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:05.020 --> 00:17:06.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] You poor soul.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:06.950 --> 00:17:09.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I can hear everything
they're saying.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:09.530 --> 00:17:10.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[STARK] Oh, well.
-Huh.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:11.450 --> 00:17:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was all worth it,
since she likes it so much.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:16.670 --> 00:17:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:19.210 --> 00:17:20.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Attaboy.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:20.290 --> 00:17:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To tell you the truth,
I didn’t think</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:21.670 --> 00:17:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you had it in you to make
such a romantic statement.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:24.420 --> 00:17:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Huh?
[SEIN] That design</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is of a mirrored lotus.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:27.130 --> 00:17:29.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the language of flowers,
it means "eternal love."</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:29.930 --> 00:17:30.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Around these parts,</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:31.010 --> 00:17:32.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it’s a common symbol
to give to a lover.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:33.010 --> 00:17:34.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000363
00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:36.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mister Stark?</b></Default>

c0000364
00:17:36.560 --> 00:17:37.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had no idea, okay?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:39.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It’s all a misunderstanding.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:40.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I’ve got
the first clue</b></Default>

c0000367
00:17:40.690 --> 00:17:41.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the language of flowers?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:17:42.020 --> 00:17:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, of course not.
You’re an idiot.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:17:44.390 --> 00:17:46.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You’re being
even meaner than usual!</b></Default>

c0000370
00:17:47.320 --> 00:17:49.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not like you’re some
flower genius, either.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:17:49.700 --> 00:17:51.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did you just say to me?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:17:51.200 --> 00:17:53.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Nothing, ma’am.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:17:54.360 --> 00:17:57.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, should I find
something to replace it?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:17:58.080 --> 00:17:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You put an incredible amount
of effort</b></Default>

c0000375
00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into picking out
the perfect gift for me.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:03.040 --> 00:18:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don’t suggest
such a thing again.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:05.500 --> 00:18:06.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I-I wouldn’t dream of it.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:12.970 --> 00:18:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Something funny?
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:15.510 --> 00:18:17.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] No, not at all.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:18.850 --> 00:18:25.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:23.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] Mistress Frieren?
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:26.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've finished repairing
the carriage.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:26.550 --> 00:19:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll depart early
tomorrow morning.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:29.300 --> 00:19:30.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Understood.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:30.800 --> 00:19:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been sneaking away
from us at night.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:33.420 --> 00:19:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it that
you’re looking for?</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:36.010 --> 00:19:37.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
The ring Himmel gave me.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:37.890 --> 00:19:39.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Let me help.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:42.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll wait to leave for town
until we've found it.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:43.680 --> 00:19:44.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That’s all right.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:45.260 --> 00:19:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we don’t have
any luck tonight,</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:46.900 --> 00:19:47.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I’ll give up.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:48.270 --> 00:19:50.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’ve grown used
to losing things.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:50.860 --> 00:19:52.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, that ring isn’t all</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:52.150 --> 00:19:53.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Himmel gave me
over the years.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:54.570 --> 00:19:55.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The design.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:55.740 --> 00:19:58.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It has a mirrored lotus
like my bracelet does.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:58.530 --> 00:20:01.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] In flower language,
that means "eternal love."</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:01.580 --> 00:20:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh. I didn't realize that.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:04.780 --> 00:20:05.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:06.170 --> 00:20:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I seriously doubt Himmel knew
what it meant, either.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:12.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless,
I'm certain it's important.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:15.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's look for it together.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:18.350 --> 00:20:20.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MERCHANT 13A] I wish
you would’ve told me sooner.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:21.140 --> 00:20:22.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Given my line of work,</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:22.510 --> 00:20:24.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I’m typically the first stop
when folks in my village</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:24.970 --> 00:20:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lose valuable jewelry.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:26.770 --> 00:20:28.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MERCHANT 13A]
This is a spell for finding</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:28.230 --> 00:20:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lost accessories.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:29.810 --> 00:20:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was intending to give it
to you as a reward</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:31.770 --> 00:20:34.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for all your assistance
with my carriage and horse.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:34.230 --> 00:20:35.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[paper rustling]
-[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:56.010 --> 00:20:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:58.050 --> 00:21:00.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To say a special thanks
for all your hard work</b></Default>

c0000416
00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:01.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on that side quest,</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:01.470 --> 00:21:03.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please choose
whatever you’d like.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:04.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Jewelry, huh?</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:06.150 --> 00:21:08.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would've preferred something
from a magic shop.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:09.230 --> 00:21:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this one will do.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:10.520 --> 00:21:11.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was too easy.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:11.850 --> 00:21:13.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should put some more
thought into it.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:14.900 --> 00:21:15.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:16.950 --> 00:21:18.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:19.700 --> 00:21:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:20.820 --> 00:21:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:44.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[HIMMEL] Frieren.
-Hm? Ah, yes.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:46.020 --> 00:21:47.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:48.980 --> 00:21:55.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000430
00:22:11.290 --> 00:22:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000431
00:22:15.830 --> 00:22:18.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cart wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000432
00:22:20.970 --> 00:22:22.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000433
00:22:22.420 --> 00:22:24.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were close
to giving up your search.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad you didn’t?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:22:28.390 --> 00:22:29.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:34.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I am.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:22:38.530 --> 00:22:39.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I meant to ask,</b></Default>

c0000438
00:22:39.740 --> 00:22:42.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why exactly are you wearing
a mirrored-lotus bracelet?</b></Default>

c0000439
00:22:43.150 --> 00:22:45.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Because Mister Stark
is an idiot.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:22:46.370 --> 00:22:47.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] No respect.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:21.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
I have battle magic, too.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:24:22.130 --> 00:24:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN] He doesn't have
his brother's talent.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:24:24.380 --> 00:24:26.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] In any case, it looks
like we should hurry.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:24:26.850 --> 00:24:28.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Let's move on
to the next village.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:24:28.510 --> 00:24:29.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This smells like trouble.</b></Default>

